0x01 - Default setting (character is not set). 0x02 - Set a character (not supported for font formatting). 0x03 - Reset all characters to default settings (not supported for font formatting). 0x04 - Apply font formatting to the selected characters only (not supported for font formatting). 0x05 - Apply font formatting to the entire selection (not supported for font formatting). 0x06 - Set the font name (not supported for font formatting). 0x07 - Set the font height (not supported for font formatting). 0x08 - Set the font style (not supported for font formatting). 0x09 - Set the font weight (not supported for font formatting). 0x0A - Set the font color index (not supported for font formatting). 0x0B - Set the font formatting options.